FBIS4-61511 "drsov088_a_94035" FBIS-SOV-94-088 Daily Report 6 May 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Russians To Be Evacuated From Yemen Russians To Be Evacuated From Yemen LD0605125594 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1049 GMT 6 May 94 LD0605125594 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] An Il-76 plane of the Russian Ministry for Emergencies is flying off from the Zhukovskiy airport at Moscow at around 13:00 Friday to Djibouti in the Horn of Africa to pick up Russians in Yemen, where fighting is continuing between troops from the north and south of that state in southern Arabia, a ministry spokesman has reported to Interfax.
